    "In this phase, the task is to determine the type of content generation required, such as customized descriptions of costumes, translation between languages, text summarization, synthetic data generation, music creation from lyrics, or providing rapid responses by generating answers for customers.The second phase involves determining the intellectual data necessary for effectively customizing the model.",
